      "span_text": "A constant amount of RNA was reverse transcribed with random primers (Promega, Madison, WI) and Moloney murine leukemia virus (MMLV) reverse transcriptase (Promega) as described.  DNase-and RNase-free water (Ambion, Austin, TX) was added to obtain a final concentration equivalent of 10 ng RNA/L and 5 L used for quantitative reverse-transcription-polymerase chain reaction (QRT-PCR).",
